Feb 6 (Reuters) - Natco Pharma Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER CONSOL NET PROFIT 2.18 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS PROFIT 1.95 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* RECOMMENDED DIVIDEND OF 7 RUPEES PER SHARE * DEC QUARTER CONSOL REVENUE FROM OPERATIONS 5.62 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 6.79 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
